{"tid":1160673,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成日講西客多，有冇人真係有俾服務人員西過嘅經歷？","createTime":"2019-05-18T15:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T22:08:39.000Z","uid":187852,"like":0,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c3b40e13f4dcddbb7f58b6e8bfb7547ef7945de3","tid":1160673,"uid":187852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T15:49:31.000Z","msg":"拋磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 紅磡海濱南岸間OK<br />\n<br />\n因為最近都係得海濱南岸呢間CircleK，所以就入咗去喇。入面唔多人，兩三個客到，櫃檯有個40𡃁歲𡃁肥女人係到，咁我就揀左3個啫喱去櫃檯比錢，Total 大約$25到。事關我想唱散張$500都唔過份姐，便利店唔會幾張$100都無掛？咁我就好聲好氣問佢喇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我     <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />肥婆收銀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「唔好意思我得$500。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （摷一摷銀櫃）：「無喎。找唔到比你喎。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「Err..你可唔可以幫我睇下隔離機有冇？」（櫃檯兩部機，隔離機無人）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（一面不滿）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵搵下又比佢搵到有$100紙咁就要唱返錢比另外一部機到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「唔好意思呀！啱啱唔知隔離機有錢找。唔好意思呀！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「哦哦⋯唔緊要唔緊要。」<br />\n<br />\n我心諗都唔係第一日見佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我聽佢係咁唔好意思咁，語氣都唔係話好，不過算啦心諗又唔洗道晒歉咁咁誇張找到錢咪得囉。<br />\n<br />\n去到找錢真係唔知Jm9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢好誇張咁數返一百二百三百四百比我，咁我又要拎住3個啫喱又多散紙咁塞唔切入銀包，佢望咗兩秒一手搶咗我疊銀紙然後又用啲好誇張嘅動作疊啲紙，又好撚誇張咁雙手遞比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但完全feel到個動作係串緊你叫你快啲走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心撚jm9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都係唱個錢姐dllm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1edfdd61856a6cb84e575cc780b7bb0fec539e4b","tid":1160673,"uid":187852,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T15:56:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef6757edb562626f09c3f70b94ecd6bcbcf7fb2","tid":1160673,"uid":187852,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T16:05:18.000Z","msg":"無人有？"},{"pid":"d3f5dea714f4c4a5c4ec11694c5b274bc773cf6d","tid":1160673,"uid":187852,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T16:13:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e7b5433a49679a3d555f86ddbc97ecfee6a6131","tid":1160673,"uid":7078,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T16:16:24.000Z","msg":"樓豬講緊自己係西客？"},{"pid":"6025635c94bbc981dd6cfa20bc17b9dd8b8289a0","tid":1160673,"uid":208241,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T16:20:12.000Z","msg":"去audi睇車，想問佢攞price list<br />\n比佢用西語氣問:究竟想睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 當時tshirt 短褲 人字拖 19歲"},{"pid":"71797e3e5f2966e3436e1abd25bf63882c38de60","tid":1160673,"uid":97840,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T16:27:13.000Z","msg":"買25蚊野好意思用500蚊出黎唱？"},{"pid":"f51d4ab8f00828dbe95545d35c374f0381d62015","tid":1160673,"uid":165939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T16:32:19.000Z","msg":"我依家日日都西緊我啲客<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b35ada6ba29dde63212284ebd2d14e0428d420f","tid":1160673,"uid":193476,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T16:45:58.000Z","msg":"最西都只係有次見到間野入面明明有好多位<br />\n同門口個待應講「兩位，唔該」<